| [get_deals](file:///d:/AI_Orchestration/mcp_server/crm/tools.py#63-86) | `access_token, status_filter` | POSTs to `N8N_WEBHOOK_CRM` → formats deal list |
| [get_tasks](file:///d:/AI_Orchestration/mcp_server/crm/tools.py#87-110) | `access_token, deal_id` | POSTs to `N8N_WEBHOOK_CRM` → formats task list |
| [get_task_comments](file:///d:/AI_Orchestration/mcp_server/crm/tools.py#111-134) | `access_token, task_id` | POSTs to `N8N_WEBHOOK_CRM` → formats comment thread |
| [get_checklists](file:///d:/AI_Orchestration/mcp_server/crm/tools.py#137-162) | `access_token, task_id` | POSTs to `N8N_WEBHOOK_CRM` → formats checklist items |
| [get_subtasks](file:///d:/AI_Orchestration/mcp_server/crm/tools.py#165-190) | `access_token, task_id` | POSTs to `N8N_WEBHOOK_CRM` → formats child tasks |
| [get_approvals](file:///d:/AI_Orchestration/mcp_server/crm/tools.py#193-218) | `access_token, task_id` | POSTs to `N8N_WEBHOOK_CRM` → formats approval statuses |
| [get_time_tracking](file:///d:/AI_Orchestration/mcp_server/crm/tools.py#221-247) | `access_token, task_id` | POSTs to `N8N_WEBHOOK_CRM` → formats time entries |

#### Automation ([mcp_server/automation/tools.py](file:///d:/AI_Orchestration/mcp_server/automation/tools.py))
| Tool | Args | What it does |
|---|---|---|
| [create_task](file:///d:/AI_Orchestration/mcp_server/automation/tools.py#63-91) | `access_token, deal_id, title, description` | POSTs to `N8N_WEBHOOK_AUTOMATION` → confirms creation |
| [send_notification](file:///d:/AI_Orchestration/mcp_server/automation/tools.py#92-120) | `access_token, recipient, message, channel` | POSTs to `N8N_WEBHOOK_AUTOMATION` → confirms send |

