## 5. Project File Structure

```
AI_Orchestration/
├── .env                          ← Environment variables
├── main.py                       ← FastAPI application entry point
├── requirements.txt              ← Python dependencies
│
├── app/
│   ├── config.py                 ← Settings (loads .env)
│   ├── security.py               ← Auth, rate limiting, sanitization
│   ├── utils.py                  ← get_gemini_llm() factory
│   ├── mcp_client.py             ← Multi-server MCP client
│   └── graphs/
│       ├── state.py              ← AgentState TypedDict
│       └── supervisor.py         ← ReAct agent graph
│
└── mcp_server/
    ├── start_all.py              ← Launches all 3 MCP servers
    ├── shared/
    │   └── llm_helper.py         ← Shared Gemini helper
    ├── knowledge/
    │   ├── server.py             ← FastMCP on :8081
    │   └── tools.py              ← rag_search
    ├── crm/
    │   ├── server.py             ← FastMCP on :8082
    │   └── tools.py              ← get_deals, get_tasks, get_task_comments
    └── automation/
        ├── server.py             ← FastMCP on :8083
        └── tools.py              ← create_task, send_notification
```
